Package com.neatnodes.algorithm

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Innovation
    A class used by an InnovationManager to track genetic innovations.
    InnovationManager
    A class that tracks the innovations that occur each generation and provides innovation numbers to use for new Connections created as part of the NEAT algorithm.
    Simulation
    Provides entry point methods for the library.
    Species
    A class used to group together Genomes that are sufficiently similar to each other.
    StaticFunctions
    This class provides static methods that implement the behaviour required by the NEAT algorithm.
